{"tid":1869931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎》哈佛權威：新型冠狀病毒是進攻性生物武器","createTime":"2020-02-08T12:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T13:04:58.000Z","uid":73092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e1c04bc22fd4f60d3992a1be738b518bd59ce68","tid":1869931,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:44:27.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國哈佛大學法學博士弗朗西斯．博伊爾（Francis Boyle）過去曾起草美國《生物武器法》，他最近談論中國武漢肺炎疫情時，認為新型冠狀病毒（2019-nCoV）是基因改造出來的進攻性生物武器。<br />\n<br />\n弗朗西斯．博伊爾接受《地緣政治與帝國》（Geopolitics &amp; Empire）專訪時，討論在中國武漢爆發的冠狀病毒和當地的「生物安全4級實驗室（BSL-4，中國民間稱P4病毒實驗室）」，他認為，這種病毒具有潛在的致命性，是一種具有功能性的基因改造生物進攻性武器，或兩用生物戰武器。<br />\n<br />\n弗朗西斯．博伊爾認為，這就是中國政府最初試圖掩蓋這種病毒的原因，中方現在也正採取嚴厲措施加以遏制消息傳播，武漢「生物安全4級實驗室」還是世界衛生組織（WHO）專門指定的研究實驗室，博伊爾強調，世衛組織完全了解目前正在發生的事情。<br />\n<br />\n弗朗西斯．博伊爾（Francis Boyle）是美國哈佛法學院博士，還獲得哈佛大學的政治學博士學位，他曾在人權、戰爭罪行和種族滅絕、核政策和生物戰領域，為眾多國際機構提供建議，曾任國際特赦組織董事會成員，起草美國《生物武器法》，該法被稱為《 1989年生物武器反恐法》，當時得到美國會兩院的一致批准，並由小布希（George Walker Bush）總統簽署成法。"},{"pid":"b3eea2585ad95de4dc181dc08fe42f1dc5e60c31","tid":1869931,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3061047?fbclid=IwAR2CstmHjcl44z1HJdCulGZS05Z0S3KbLiORU_QBdQI4LRxFiL-ySz_gs0o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3061047%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2CstmHjcl44z1HJdCulGZS05Z0S3KbLiORU_QBdQI4LRxFiL-ySz_gs0o&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOpnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=1b242746\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3061047%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2CstmHjcl44z1HJdCulGZS05Z0S3KbLiORU_QBdQI4LRxFiL-ySz_gs0o&h=b11f43a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3061047?fbclid=IwAR2CstmHjcl44z1HJdCulGZS05Z0S3KbLiORU_QBdQI4LRxFiL-ySz_gs0o</a>"},{"pid":"9885b8ada7815ff55a5044d89f51928ec63b8773","tid":1869931,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:45:12.000Z","msg":"中國生化武器專家進駐武漢P4實驗室 網友：開始相信陰謀論了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1869925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1869925</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d386991d4d2612ef5d09b99a767fe37b1fe520d","tid":1869931,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f44cde7d284f0b9d03634f29b205994ed8dda0","tid":1869931,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:46:10.000Z","msg":"仲叫支那肺炎?改口叫支那化武啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfd80efa6df2d2009a229324166be51f5614363","tid":1869931,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"香港人集唔到會，遊唔到行，但都重有方法可以繼續場抗爭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1869924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1869924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}